author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Scout24 uses proceeds from IPO for debt repayment
text:
Oct 26 Scout24 AG :
* Uses proceeds from IPO for debt repayment
* Debt repayment of 214 million euros ($235.91 million)
* Annual interest burden will be approximately 9.1 million euros lower Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.9071 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom)
